Convert a wordpress blog (or more accurately a WordPress XML Export File) to html files.

I used this to migrate my wordpress blog to evernote (by dragging the resulting files into evernote).


# Notes:
# - currently does not handle images, attachments or comments
# - was tested on MacOS X (10.5 & 10.6)
# - not "carefully" developed e.g. poor exception handling, little testing, ...

See Adam Morris' version which creates a single evernote import file:
https://github.com/adammorris/Luis-Rei-Wordpress-to-Evernote
